---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Get to know the creator behind Skyroute Enterprise‚Äîthe personal studio that powers the YouTube channel and immersive website experience."
  ogImage="/videos/og-placeholder.svg"
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-20">
    <div class="space-y-6 text-white">
      <span data-pill>Behind the lens</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold leading-tight sm:text-5xl">A personal studio built to document ambitious ideas</h1>
      <p class="text-base text-slate-300">
        Skyroute Enterprise is both a portfolio and a live journal. Every production is filmed, edited, and shared in sync across the website
        and the YouTube channel so the audience can follow the craft in real time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div data-surface class="space-y-4 p-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">What drives the work</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
          Story-led technology. Each episode explores how immersive media, lighting, and sound design can trigger emotion. The personal site keeps extended notes while YouTube captures the momentum.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div data-surface class="space-y-4 p-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Signature aesthetics</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
          Neon gradients, glassy surfaces, and generous negative space. The goal is cohesion‚Äîwhether it is a video frame or a page layout, the same palette guides the experience.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div data-surface class="space-y-4 p-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">How content ships</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
          Each project receives a long-form article, an annotated gallery, and a YouTube release. Members receive bonus LUT packs, color grading walkthroughs, and behind-the-scenes instrumentals.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr,1fr] lg:items-start">
      <div class="space-y-6 text-white">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Timeline</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-6 text-sm text-slate-300">
          <li>
            <p class="text-white">2021 ‚Äî Channel launch</p>
            <p>The YouTube channel debuts with build logs that mirror the same bold typography and gradients as the personal homepage.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="text-white">2022 ‚Äî Projection residencies</p>
            <p>Immersive installations begin touring festivals. Each stop earns its own microsite section with interactive timelines.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="text-white">2023 ‚Äî Live grading sessions</p>
            <p>Weekly livestreams and watch parties bring the community into the grading bay, matching the website‚Äôs glassmorphism UI.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="text-white">2024 ‚Äî Unified brand refresh</p>
            <p>The redesign you are browsing‚Äîtying YouTube, newsletter, and website together with a single neon noir identity.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div data-surface class="space-y-5 p-8 text-slate-300">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Toolkit & collaborators</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 text-[#ff9fb0]">‚ñπ</span> Cinema cameras, FPV rigs, and volumetric capture pipelines.</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 text-[#ff9fb0]">‚ñπ</span> Custom TouchDesigner patches for projection mapping.</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 text-[#ff9fb0]">‚ñπ</span> Collaborations with musicians, choreographers, and lighting designers.</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 text-[#ff9fb0]">‚ñπ</span> Cloudflare Workers + Astro for rapid microsite launches.</li>
        </ul>
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@skyrouteenterprise.com"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/20 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:border-white/40"
        >
          <span aria-hidden="true">ü§ù</span>
          Discuss a collaboration
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
